Enable RDP (Remote Desktop) on Ubuntu:

  Install NoMachine:
    cd Desktop
    wget wget https://download.nomachine.com/download/6.12/Linux/nomachine_6.12.3_7_amd64.deb
    sudo dpkg -i nomachine_6.12.3_7_amd64.deb
    
Be sure to always check for latest version here:
  https://www.nomachine.com/download/linux&id=1
